    <bug_when>2013-04-12 17:00:46 -0400</bug_when>
    <thetext>Steps:
1. Invoke OperationsUtil.execute()
2. Interrupt the current thread while the request is in progress

Result: The method returns but the request is not aborted. This can cause a connection leak from the connection pool.

Expected result: The request is aborted.</thetext>
  </long_desc><long_desc isprivate="0" >
