    <comment_count>1</comment_count>
    <who name="Steffen Pingel">steffen.pingel</who>
    <bug_when>2013-05-09 13:40:21 -0400</bug_when>
    <thetext>Instead of reading executing HTTP operations and reading streams on a separate thread a monitor thread should detect cancellation and close the socket. That reduces resource consumption and simplifies the HttpClient interaction since only one thread accesses the connection.</thetext>
